Homewood Canyon first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]]<ref name=2000CensusCA/> formed along with the [[Valley Wells, California|Valley Wells CDP]] and the [[Trona, Inyo County, California|Trona CDP]] out of the dissolved [[Homewood Canyon-Valley Wells, California|Homewood Canyon-Valley Wells CDP]].<ref name=2010CensusCA/>

===2020===
The [[2020 United States census]] reported that Homewood Canyon had a population of 40. The [[population density]] was {{convert|3.9|/sqmi}}. The racial makeup of Homewood Canyon was 34 (85%) [[White Americans|White]] and six (15%) from two or more races. There were four (10%) [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] people of any race.<ref name=DP1>{{cite web |title=Homewood Canyon CDP, California; DP1: Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDP2020.DP1?g=1600000US0634405 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=June 22, 2025}}</ref>

There were 18 households, out of which seven (39%) had children under the age of 18 living in them, eight (44%) were married-couple households, four (22%) were [[cohabitation|cohabiting]] couple households, zero (0%) had a female householder with no partner present, and six (33%) had a male householder with no partner present. Four households (22%) were one person, and three (17%) were one person aged 65 or older. The average household size was 2.22.<ref name=DP1/> There were 11 [[family (U.S. Census)|families]] (61% of all households).<ref>{{cite web |title=Homewood Canyon CDP, California; P16: Household Type - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDHC2020.P16?g=1600000US0634405 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=June 22, 2025}}</ref>

The age distribution was nine people (23%) under the age of 18, zero people (0%) aged 18 to 24, eight people (20%) aged 25 to 44, 14 people (35%) aged 45 to 64, and nine people (23%) who were 65{{nbsp}}years of age or older. The median age was 55.5{{nbsp}}years. There were 22 males and 18 females.<ref name=DP1/>

There were 34 housing units at an average density of {{convert|3.3|/mi2}}, of which 18 (53%) were occupied. Of these, 13 (72%) were owner-occupied, and five (28%) were occupied by renters.<ref name=DP1/>

